text.tspan: Flows to manage scene collections in OBS Studio. Scene collections are managed in a separate
dialog. The menu is moved to the scenes dock.
Scenes dock contains a menu button for scene
- Opens the dialog to manage collections
- Sort by name or recently used
- Focused by default the the dialog is created
- Typing anywhere on the window starts search
- Pressing enter activates the first item of the list
- Row activates on single click (left click)
- Ctrl + R initiates renaming of the focused row
Kinda meh but we won't judge
- Pressing Shift while nagivating selects range
- Enter or Space selects focused item
- Delete button goes inactive if active scene seletect
